        <abstract>
            <p>Comments on CD’s health.</p> 
<p>Has received gold medal from Dutch Academy of Science for <hi rend="italic">Zur Entwicklungsgeschichte der Siphonophoren</hi> [1869].</p>  
<p>His <hi rend="italic">Entstehung des Menschengeschlechts</hi> [1868] has been sharply attacked by the clergy.</p> 
